data.description:
Enjoy the Air Wherever You Roam Featuring the first Max Air unit designed for a Nike Sportswear lifestyle sneaker, the Air Max 270 features a hefty Visible Max Air comfort bubble that wraps 270 degrees around the heel. It's also the tallest Max Air unit ever (32 mm) to provide extra cushioning when you're covering a lot of ground. And you'll be striding in legendary style, as this distinctive shoe combines design elements of the iconic Air Max 180 from 1991 and 1993's popular Air Max 93. A Real Athletic Feel Sneakerheads looking for a casual street shoe also want to be sure their footwear is built to stand up to real-life conditions. Athletic performance features, durable materials, and modern construction methods result in a tough, everyday sneaker that feels lightweight and cool, provides a firm fit and delivers all-day comfort. Nike Air Max 270 Features: Breathable mesh upper with synthetic overlays for durability. Rubber toe tip provides extra durability in a high-wear areas. Neoprene bootie ensures foot-hugging fit. Dual-density foam midsole cushions forefoot and midfoot. Large Visible Max Air unit adds extra heel protection. Rubber waffle tread provides good traction.
